@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_undavb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.94
    v2 = ((0.90 * wp.sin(v0 + 0.07)) - ((v0 + 0.75 + v0 + 0.48) * (v2 + 0.67 * v2 + 0.29)))
    v1 = wp.abs(0.08)
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.cos((tmp + 0.51 - v1 + 0.09)))
    data[tid] = v0
